# Agent Chaos Runbook

## Port-forward nhanh

```bash
# Local kubeconfig
kubectl port-forward svc/my-grafana 3000:80 -n monitoring
kubectl port-forward svc/chaos-dashboard 2333:2333 -n chaos-mesh

# k3s server
sudo k3s kubectl port-forward svc/chaos-dashboard 8080:2333 -n chaos-mesh --address 0.0.0.0
sudo k3s kubectl port-forward svc/my-grafana 3000:80 -n monitoring --address 0.0.0.0
```

## Ke hoach chaos 24h

- Runbook chi tiet: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-24h-plan.md`
- Huong dan chay: `LAB_CENTER/agent/HUONG_DAN_CHAOS_MESH_VA_PYTHON_METRICS.md`
- Manifest: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/`
- Label terms: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-labeling-terms.md`
- Label rules YAML: `LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-labeling-rules.yaml`

Chay 24h schedule mode (khong chay chung voi immediate mode):

```bash
kctl(){ if command -v k3s >/dev/null 2>&1 && [[ -r /etc/rancher/k3s/k3s.yaml ]]; then sudo k3s kubectl "$@"; else kubectl "$@"; fi; }
kctl apply -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/00-common-labels.yaml
kctl apply -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/01-chaos-target-nginx.yaml
kctl rollout status deploy/chaos-target-nginx -n backend --timeout=120s
kctl apply -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/30-schedules-24h.yaml
```

Luu y: IOChaos da duoc cau hinh inject tren `/mnt/chaos`, khong inject vao root filesystem `/`.
Khong `kubectl apply -f` ca thu muc vi se tao ca immediate chaos (`10/11/20/21`) va schedule cung luc, de xay ra xung dot tc/ipset.

Xem trang thai:

```bash
kctl get iochaos,networkchaos,dnschaos,stresschaos,schedules -n backend
```

Cleanup:

```bash
kctl delete -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/30-schedules-24h.yaml --ignore-not-found
kctl delete -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/21-dns-chaos.yaml --ignore-not-found
kctl delete -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/20-network-chaos.yaml --ignore-not-found
kctl delete -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/11-disk-stress-and-fill.yaml --ignore-not-found
kctl delete -f LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-mesh-manifests/10-disk-iochaos.yaml --ignore-not-found
```

## Tao dataset metric + label (30s)

```bash
python LAB_CENTER/agent/main.py \
	--prom-url http://localhost:9090 \
	--start 2026-03-20T00:00:00 \
	--end 2026-03-21T00:00:00 \
	--step 30s \
	--rules LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos-labeling-rules.yaml \
	--output LAB_CENTER/agent/chaos_labeled_30s.csv
```
